\b \cf2 Rio Bus
\b0  is a collaborative real-time bus monitoring tool that uses the open API provided by Rio de Janeiro's City Hall and FETRANSPOR. Our main goal is to help the citizen, either a resident or a visitor, to get around in the city of Rio de Janeiro.\
