\fs40 \cf2 How does it work?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl320\qj\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf2 Just type in the search bar the bus line that you want to find or a related keyword (e.g. Copacabana) and the position of each bus will be shown on the map.\
\
On the bottom of the screen, you'll find information such as the bus line name and an option to filter the direction, if available. You can also find more information about each vehicle by tapping the markers on the map.\
